# STATS::PLAYSTATS_SPIN_WHEEL

## Summary
Metric fires at the end of the wheel spin (when the player choses to play only - do not send a metric if the player never pushes x to stop the wheel after being knocked out)

## Parameters
* **INT** contentId
* **INT** spintType
* **INT** rewardType
* **INT** rewardItem
